    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Gold golems are extravagant constructs, crafted at great expense at the command of the rich and powerful. They\u2019re most often used to guard palaces and family vaults, but are rarely placed in areas that are hidden away from casual observation. <br/><br/>Many of those who expend the funds to create a gold golem aren\u2019t the type to hide the conspicuous display of their wealth from their visitors. A gold golem is humanoid in appearance, standing 10 feet tall and weighing 4,500 pounds."
        }
    ],
